      propertyPath: E
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 975163904}
    - target: {fileID: 7716988434102719772, guid: c3e0e0b0eda2ce6409aad1f6f3c107b6, type: 3}
      propertyPath: Dialogtext
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 267284893}
    - target: {fileID: 7716988434102719772, guid: c3e0e0b0eda2ce6409aad1f6f3c107b6, type: 3}
      propertyPath: strings.Array.size
      value: 7
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7716988434102719772, guid: c3e0e0b0eda2ce6409aad1f6f3c107b6, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'strings.Array.data[0]'
      value: I used to live down on the lower levels
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7716988434102719772, guid: c3e0e0b0eda2ce6409aad1f6f3c107b6, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'strings.Array.data[1]'
      value: But most people have left the building now due to the killings
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7716988434102719772, guid: c3e0e0b0eda2ce6409aad1f6f3c107b6, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'strings.Array.data[2]'
      value: So everyone who remains have moved to the top levels for the sunlight
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7716988434102719772, guid: c3e0e0b0eda2ce6409aad1f6f3c107b6, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'strings.Array.data[3]'
      value: 'Most lower rooms lack windows. '
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7716988434102719772, guid: c3e0e0b0eda2ce6409aad1f6f3c107b6, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'strings.Array.data[4]'
      value: So lamps is the only source of light down there.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7716988434102719772, guid: c3e0e0b0eda2ce6409aad1f6f3c107b6, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'strings.Array.data[5]'
      value: well, used to be the only source of light...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7716988434102719772, guid: c3e0e0b0eda2ce6409aad1f6f3c107b6, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'strings.Array.data[6]'
      value: final
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 9134838061695229791, guid: c3e0e0b0eda2ce6409aad1f6f3c107b6, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_Name
      value: DialogTrigger (2)
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
